{"tid":1453080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"cctvb新聞部現逃亡潮 四分一前線記者遞信請辭","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:42:29.000Z","uid":68738,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93c6545aa9f5b1136523c0f2a78d5a44fbb32d72","tid":1453080,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190812/large/1565578191_4c2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190812%2Flarge%2F1565578191_4c2f.png&h=30b375b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPok&eacute;mon GO HK嘅版主今朝都開post，報道張家灝辭職消息。小圖為Pok&eacute;mon GO HK fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n特區政府堅拒接納市民五大訴求，反修例運動持續，被唔少網民認定係紅媒嘅大台無綫電視都受針對，八方聽聞，cctvb新聞部喺反修例浪潮下出現逃亡潮，約近四分一前線記者已經交信辭職，唔知係不滿大台報道方針或手法、抑或覺得用大台身份去採訪好有壓力？而交咗信準備走人嘅，據知仲包括噚晚喺銅鑼灣示威現場採訪期間，喺出現疑似警察扮示威者、混入人群撞黑衣人時，上前質問疑似便衣警「係咪阿Sir？」嘅張家灝，呢一幕獲網民力讚兼廣傳。<br />\n<br />\nFb專頁Pok&eacute;mon GO HK嘅版主今朝都開post，報道張家灝辭職消息，讚對方多次喺記者會問得好狠，包括質過特首林鄭：「例如『係咪撤回呢兩個字唯獨唔可以出自你把口呢？』」。據了解，張家灝喺較早前已經交信辭職；八方今早向佢查詢，佢話不便回應。<br />\n<br />\n前線記者真係唔易做，呢排頻頻因為採訪食摧淚彈，仲要被警方無理對待，緊守崗位但若再遭示威者指罵，都咪話唔心灰意冷。八方聽聞，ccctvb新聞部廿幾名前線記者中，約四分一人相繼辭職，絕大部份仲係已有幾年經驗嘅記者，由流失數字，或者都呈現一啲事實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922608&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=66382549\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922608&h=e36c5941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922608</a>"},{"pid":"71c560f935fc4ccc1df530f54cd4fd635391c3c5","tid":1453080,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:13:32.000Z","msg":"未走個d 死全家"},{"pid":"8cdb421e50c86c242119c8da788e9ee07a25b1d6","tid":1453080,"uid":57891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777e5e293288d0647ca605c9e62f4bd0231147d0","tid":1453080,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"原來之前出post屌佢果d全部係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce506e6c6d049a6fcdb671bb7392dbfb426b0dd9","tid":1453080,"uid":237106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"調條臭雞金盈出去做前線囉"},{"pid":"f87ccb7fd33949fac993e152b34a2b06cce6fc95","tid":1453080,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"777e5e293288d0647ca605c9e62f4bd0231147d0","tid":1453080,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"原來之前出post屌佢果d全部係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"原來如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4888445db126e6c21bd81e064ac7aef9383bcd","tid":1453080,"uid":164387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:42:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}